## Class 命名规范

采用 **kebab-case 模块-元素**二级结构（非 BEM `__` `--` 风格）：

| 模块 | 示例 |
|------|------|
| 导航 | `site-nav-wrap` / `nav-brand` / `nav-brand-logo` / `nav-brand-mark` / `nav-links` |
| Hero | `hero-bg` / `hero-content` / `hero-text` / `hero-kicker` / `hero-title` / `hero-desc` / `hero-line` / `hero-stats` / `hero-stat-num` / `hero-stat-label` |
| Section | `section-head` / `section-index` / `section-title` / `section-note` |
| 项目卡片 | `project-grid` / `project-card` / `project-media` / `project-body` / `project-topline` / `project-num` / `project-tag` / `project-name` / `project-caption` / `project-chips` / `project-go` |
| 看板卡片 | `board-grid` / `board-card` / `board-no` / `board-name` / `board-status` / `board-desc` |
| 结尾 | `closing` / `closing-title` / `closing-text` |
| 状态类 | `.scrolled` / `.active` / `.visible` / `.fade-in` |
| 项目修饰符 | `.soviet` / `.nendo`（直接加在 `.project-card` 上） |

